### Stage 9 调度与运维
# 使用 local Profile 启动后按需执行。
# 调度配置请求中的来源 ID 1 请替换为实际采集员 ID。

### 1. 仪表盘汇总
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/dashboard
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage9-dashboard

> {%
client.test("仪表盘可用", function () {
  client.assert(response.status === 200, "预期 HTTP 200");
  client.assert(response.body.data.sourceCount >= 0, "应返回采集员数量");
  client.assert(Array.isArray(response.body.data.recentTasks), "应返回最近任务");
});
%}

### 2. 查询全部调度配置
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/operations/schedules
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage9-schedules

### 3. 为采集员 1 启用每 60 分钟采集
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/operations/schedules/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage9-schedule-save

{"enabled": true, "intervalMinutes": 60}

### 4. 立即检查到期调度
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/operations/schedules/run-due
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage9-run-due

### 5. 查询任务及触发方式
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/tasks?page=0&size=20
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage9-tasks

### 6. 创建本地备份
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/operations/backups
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage9-backup

> {%
client.test("备份创建成功", function () {
  client.assert(response.status === 200, "预期 HTTP 200");
  client.assert(response.body.data.status === "SUCCESS", "备份状态应为 SUCCESS");
  client.assert(response.body.data.sizeBytes > 0, "备份文件不应为空");
});
%}

### 7. 查询备份记录
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/operations/backups
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage9-backups

### 可选：失败任务重试（把 1 替换为 FAILED 任务 ID）
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/tasks/1/retry
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage9-retry

### 可选：取消尚未开始的任务（把 1 替换为 CREATED 任务 ID）
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/tasks/1/cancel
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage9-cancel
